reviewText: Great video of a great band!
Another great release at a great price from this proud southern band. Hopefully they'll get around to giving the rest of the studio albums the same treatment.
Ignore the naysayers: this is a great album.  Please do not consider this a replacement for One More From The Road, however, it is a great compliment to it.
Bettter than ever, wow is this a good combo both DVD and CD's
